"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ dhammikaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "They said to Venerable Dhammika:"

msgctxt "an6.54:5.2"
msgid "“pakkamatu, bhante, āyasmā dhammiko imamhāpi āvāsā;"
msgstr "“Sir, please leave this monastery."

msgctxt "an6.54:5.3"
msgid "alaṃ te idha vāsenā”ti."
msgstr "You’ve stayed here long enough.”"

